"}, "branch": {"name": "scrolling-tabs"}}, "state": "OPEN", "author": {"display_name": "Chris Billington", "uuid": "{e363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Be363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Be363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9238baf7300c41c0e7294db922899e6ad=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsCB-1.png"}}, "nickname": "cbillington", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:cbf1bc43-1dc2-477b-9e25-1a8f40fd7ee3"}, "date": "2018-04-03T02:11:43.317790+00:00"}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 42, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pullrequests/42.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pull-requests/42"}}, "title": "Scrolling dragdroptabs"}}, {"approval": {"date": "2018-03-29T19:37:56.894689+00:00", "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 42, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pullrequests/42.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pull-requests/42"}}, "title": "Scrolling dragdroptabs"}, "user": {"display_name": "Jan Werkmann", "uuid": "{44c4905c-2b90-4045-a5f1-652b8e228626}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B44c4905c-2b90-4045-a5f1-652b8e228626%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B44c4905c-2b90-4045-a5f1-652b8e228626%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:a70cc9cf-684e-4849-a61a-9ade4d7218b5/07e5095a-4741-4dc0-a462-9c7d455f961d/128"}}, "nickname": "PhyNerd", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:a70cc9cf-684e-4849-a61a-9ade4d7218b5"}}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 42, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pullrequests/42.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pull-requests/42"}}, "title": "Scrolling dragdroptabs"}}, {"comment": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pullrequests/42/comments/60284316.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pull-requests/42/_/diff#comment-60284316"}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 42, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pullrequests/42.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pull-requests/42"}}, "title": "Scrolling dragdroptabs"}, "content": {"raw": "Playing around with this on mac showed no bugs.\n\nIt might be personal taste but I think scrolling shouldn't happen with a fixed distance but rather in a away that the left most tab always sits flush with the bounding line \\(if possible\\). This way one would not have to click left/right multiple times to fully move a tab with long tab name out of and a new one into view. \n\nAlso there was some odd behavior for small window sizes that I noticed. \\(This doesn't really need fixing\\):\n\n1. If a tab is moved to a new line even if it is long enough the scroll buttons appear:  \n  ![test.gif](https://bitbucket.org/repo/xg9BdE/images/2889053505-test.gif 'test.gif')\n2. If in you move a tab inside a line the scroll buttons sometimes randomly appear and disappear:  \n  ![test2.gif](https://bitbucket.org/repo/xg9BdE/images/4059912907-test2.gif 'test2.gif')\n\n", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Playing around with this on mac showed no bugs.</p>\n<p>It might be personal taste but I think scrolling shouldn't happen with a fixed distance but rather in a away that the left most tab always sits flush with the bounding line (if possible). This way one would not have to click left/right multiple times to fully move a tab with long tab name out of and a new one into view. </p>\n<p>Also there was some odd behavior for small window sizes that I noticed. (This doesn't really need fixing):</p>\n<ol>\n<li>If a tab is moved to a new line even if it is long enough the scroll buttons appear:<br />\n<img alt=\"test.gif\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/xg9BdE/images/2889053505-test.gif\" title=\"test.gif\" /></li>\n<li>If in you move a tab inside a line the scroll buttons sometimes randomly appear and disappear:<br />\n<img alt=\"test2.gif\" src=\"data/bitbucket.org/repo/xg9BdE/images/4059912907-test2.gif\" title=\"test2.gif\" /></li>\n</ol>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-03-29T19:37:52.841311+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Jan Werkmann", "uuid": "{44c4905c-2b90-4045-a5f1-652b8e228626}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B44c4905c-2b90-4045-a5f1-652b8e228626%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B44c4905c-2b90-4045-a5f1-652b8e228626%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:a70cc9cf-684e-4849-a61a-9ade4d7218b5/07e5095a-4741-4dc0-a462-9c7d455f961d/128"}}, "nickname": "PhyNerd", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:a70cc9cf-684e-4849-a61a-9ade4d7218b5"}, "updated_on": "2018-03-29T19:37:52.930914+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 60284316}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 42, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pullrequests/42.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/pull-requests/42"}}, "title": "Scrolling dragdroptabs"}}, {"update": {"description": "Allow dragdroptabs to have scroll buttons, and use them by default.\r\n\r\nThis restores the old behaviour which allows you to have larger numbers of tabs with scrolling rather than the text being elided in the tab labels.\r\n\r\n![scroll_buttons.png](https://bitbucket.org/repo/KEMMje/images/4017131629-scroll_buttons.png)", "title": "Scrolling dragdroptabs", "destination": {"commit": {"hash": "ce1a5de04b6c", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/commit/ce1a5de04b6c.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/labscript_utils/commits/ce1a5de04b6c"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/labscript_suite/labscript_utils.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/labscript_suite/labscript_utils"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{68347210-fb1e-4b58-86c0-bd2c04396e63}ts=249922"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "labscript_utils", "full_name": "labscript_suite/labscript_utils", "uuid": "{68347210-fb1e-4b58-86c0-bd2c04396e63}"}, "branch": {"name": "default"}}, "reason": "", "source": {"commit": {"hash": "aa0d6215b7d8", "type": "commit", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/cbillington/labscript_utils/commit/aa0d6215b7d8"}, "html": {"href": "#!/cbillington/labscript_utils/commits/aa0d6215b7d8"}}}, "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/cbillington/labscript_utils"}, "html": {"href": "#!/cbillington/labscript_utils"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{455d0b5d-4852-4e4a-b8b1-f5ba77882210}ts=python"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "labscript_utils", "full_name": "cbillington/labscript_utils", "uuid": "{455d0b5d-4852-4e4a-b8b1-f5ba77882210}"}, "branch": {"name": "scrolling-tabs"}}, "state": "OPEN", "author": {"display_name": "Chris Billington", "uuid": "{e363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Be363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Be363c5a9-5075-4656-afb5-88bd6a6dceeb%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/secure.gravatar.com/avatar/9238baf7300c41c0e7294db922899e6ad=httpsavatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.netinitialsCB-1.png"}}, "nickname": "cbillington", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:cbf1bc43-1dc2-477b-9e25-1a8f40fd7ee3"}, "date": "2018-03-29T05:51:59.702147+00:00"}, "pull_request": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 42, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/